      "text": "Ethical review of the human-subjects research is transferred to QMUL's Devolved School Research Ethics Committee (DSREC, ref DSEECS25.094); the\nevaluation protocol was reviewed and approved before any participant data was collected, and the committee's conditions on consent, anonymity, and\nwithdrawal are followed",
