      "updated": 1778816866608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Users can stop the simulation from running with a simple button at any time, they can clear their market with a simple step, also, the active learning tab\nis separated from the simulation, chats are hidden unless users click on it and if anything was confusing there is a tab for them to ask questions. Also\na help button explaining how to run the tool is visible at all times",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "ICYVJ5-QrmR6GzxMZpHCn",
      "originalText": "Users can stop the simulation from running with a simple button at any time, they can clear their market with a simple step, also, the active learning tab is separated from the simulation, chats are hidden unless users click on it and if anything was confusing there is a tab for them to ask questions. Also a help button explaining how to run the tool is visible at all times",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
